  "Description": "CALLED BY: IdsMaMMRRcvdIncmSbsdyDtlCntl\n\nPROCESSING:\n                  As a part of the MA/ACA in-sourcing, this process will load the Monthly Membership (MMR) file from CMS.  This file contains monthly subsidy data at the beneficiary/member level.  Data needs to be loaded to IDS table, RCVD_INCM_SUBSDY_DTL to be included in the in the GL process for reconciliation and finanical reporting. \n\nMODIFICATIONS:\nDeveloper                          Date                 Project/Altiris #                Change Description                             Development Project    Code Reviewer            Date Reviewed\n----------------------------------      -------------------    -----------------------------------    ---------------------------------------------------------      ----------------------------------   ---------------------------------    -------------------------   \nSai Madhu Yelakkayala   11/02/2020         US-243707                     Originally Programmed                           ids_dev2                    Jeyaprasanna               2020-12-15\n\nAnnotations:\nJob Name: IdsProvLocLoad\nRead Load File created in the FKEY job\nCopy Stage for buffer\nUpdate then Insert RCVD_INCM_SBSDY_DTL table\nLoad rejects are redirected into a Reject file"
